11#include "ipf.h"
12
13alist_t *
14load_url(char *url)
15{
16 alist_t *hosts = NULL;
17
18 if (strncmp(url, "file://", 7) == 0) {
19 /*
20 * file:///etc/passwd
21 * ^------------s
22 */
23 hosts = load_file(url);
24
25 } else if (*url == '/' || *url == '.') {
26 hosts = load_file(url);
27
28 } else if (strncmp(url, "http://", 7) == 0) {
29 hosts = load_http(url);
30 }
31
32 return hosts;
33}
